This RDF triple is then added to your Knowledge Graph.


Responsibilities of each cell
Cell	                 Responsibility	                                                   Output
Cell 8	Extract all hyperlinks (doc:wiki, doc:Temp_Import) from the XML content	Hyperlink records
Cell 9	Find the sentence containing each hyperlink and clean the sentence	Sentence records
Cell 13	Use the LLM to understand the sentence and infer the semantic relationship (predicate) between the source page and the hyperlink	Semantic triples (subject, predicate, object)
Cell 14	Convert the semantic triples into RDF triples for storage and graph construction	RDF triples
